{"title_page": "2019 Campbell Fighting Camels soccer team", "text_new": "{{Infobox NCAA team season\n| sport = soccer\n| year = 2019\n| team = Campbell Fighting Camels\n| logo = Campbell Fighting Camels logo.svg\n| logo_size = 200\n| logo_alt = \n| image = \n| image_size = \n| image_alt = \n| conference = Big South Conference\n| short_conf = Big South\n| record = 17\u20133\u20132\n| conf_record = 8\u20130\u20130\n| NSCAARank = 24\n| TDSRank = \n| head_coach = Dustin Fonder\n| hc_year = 5th\n| asst_coach1 = Alistair Moore\n| ac1_year = 1st\n| asst_coach2 = Ryan Hanson\n| ac2_year = 2nd\n| captain  =\n| captain2 =\n| captain3 = \n| stadium = Eakes Athletic Complex\n| champion = Big South regular season champions<br>Big South tournament champions\n| tourney        = NCAA Tournament\n| tourney_result = Second Round\n| prev_year = 2018\n| next_year = 2020\n}}\n{{2019 Big South Conference men's soccer standings}}\nThe '''2019 Campbell Fighting Camels soccer team''' represented [[Campbell University]] during the [[2019 NCAA Division I men's soccer season]] and the [[2019 Big South Conference men's soccer season]]. The regular season began on August 30 and concluded on November 2. It was the program's 57th season fielding a men's varsity soccer team, and their 9th season since rejoining the [[Big South Conference]]. The 2019 season was Dustin Fonder's fifth year as head coach for the program.\n\n== Roster ==\n{{updated|March 30, 2020}}<ref>{{cite web |title=2019 Men's Soccer Roster |url=https://gocamels.com/sports/mens-soccer/roster/2019|website=gocamels.com |publisher=Campbell Athletics |accessdate=March 30, 2020}}</ref>\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player | no=0  | nat=MEX | pos=GK | name=Samuel Lechuga}}\n{{Fs player | no=1  | nat=USA | pos=GK | name=Matt Karasinski}}\n{{Fs player | no=2  | nat=ENG | pos=DF | name=Edward Fulwood}}\n{{Fs player | no=3  | nat=GHA | pos=DF | name=Moses Mensah}}\n{{Fs player | no=4  | nat=FRA | pos=DF | name=Franck Momo}}\n{{Fs player | no=5  | nat=FRA | pos=DF | name=Bissafi Dotte}}\n{{Fs player | no=6  | nat=GER | pos=MF | name=Gideon Betz}}\n{{Fs player | no=7  | nat=USA | pos=MF | name=Jalen James}}\n{{Fs player | no=8  | nat=ENG | pos=MF | name=Ian Rees}}\n{{Fs player | no=9  | nat=USA | pos=FW | name=Alex Egeonu}}\n{{Fs player | no=10 | nat=USA | pos=FW | name=Adrian Morales}}\n{{Fs player | no=12 | nat=USA | pos=MF | name=Caleb Martinez}}\n{{Fs player | no=13 | nat=USA | pos=MF | name=Tyler Young}}\n{{Fs player | no=15 | nat=GHA | pos=MF | name=George Bediko}}\n{{Fs mid}}\n{{Fs player | no=16 | nat=ENG | pos=MF | name=Matt Lock}}\n{{Fs player | no=18 | nat=FRA | pos=FW | name=Thibaut Jacquel}}\n{{Fs player | no=19 | nat=USA | pos=FW | name=Dailyn Crawley}}\n{{Fs player | no=21 | nat=GHA | pos=FW | name=Emmanuel Owusu}}\n{{Fs player | no=22 | nat=USA | pos=FW | name=Aigbekan Nosegbe}}\n{{Fs player | no=23 | nat=GER | pos=MF | name=Eren Elbustu}}\n{{Fs player | no=24 | nat=USA | pos=MF | name=Humberto Chavez}}\n{{Fs player | no=25 | nat=ESP | pos=MF | name=Alemu Mercer-Miko}}\n{{Fs player | no=26 | nat=USA | pos=DF | name=Dylan Sadler}}\n{{Fs player | no=27 | nat=USA | pos=DF | name=Braden Teller}}\n{{Fs player | no=30 | nat=USA | pos=DF | name=Luka Lazarevic}}\n{{Fs player | no=37 | nat=ESP | pos=GK | name=Edu Rodriguez}}\n{{Fs player | no=38 | nat=USA | pos=GK | name=Peter Gilder}}\n\n{{Fs end}}\n\n== Schedule ==\n\nSource:<ref>{{cite web|url=https://gocamels.com/sports/mens-soccer/schedule/2019|website=gocamels.com|accessdate=March 29, 2019|title=2019 Men's Soccer Schedule|publisher=Campbell Athletics}}</ref>\n{{CSOC schedule start|rank=yes|attend=yes|goalscorers=no}}\n|-\n!colspan=6 style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Campbell Fighting Camels|color=#FFFFFF|border=0}}\"| Non-conference regular season\n|-\n{{CSOC schedule entry\n| w/l/t        = l\n| date         = August 30\n| time         = 8:00 p.m.\n| tv           = \n| nonconf      = yes\n| rank         = \n| away         = yes\n| neutral      = \n| oppra