 Pictures]] || style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[Illumination Mac Guff]] || N/A || Theatrical release\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 5 || ''[[Hop (film)#Home media|Phil's Dance Party]] || align=\"right\" | {{dts|2012|3|23}} || style=\"text-align:center;\" | Universal Pictures Home Entertainment || style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[Rhythm and Hues Studios|Rhythm and Hues]] || ''[[Hop (film)|Hop]]'' || Home video release\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 6 || ''[[The Lorax (film)#Mini-movies|Wagon Ho!]]'' || align=\"right\" rowspan=\"3\" | {{dts|2012|8|7}} || rowspan= \"9\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | Universal Pictures Home Entertainment || rowspan=\"21\" style=\"text-align:center;\" | Illumination Mac Guff || rowspan=\"3\" | ''[[The Lorax (film)|Dr. Seuss' The Lorax]]'' || rowspan=\"9\" | Home video release\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 7 || ''[[The Lorax (film)#Mini-movies|Forces of Nature]]''\n|-\n| align=\"center\" | 8 || ''[[The Lorax (film)#Mini-movies|Serenade]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 9 || ''[[Despicable Me (franchise)#Puppy (2013)|Puppy]]'' || align=\"right\" rowspan=\"3\" | {{dts|2013|12|10}} || rowspan=\"3\" | ''[[Despicable Me 2]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 10 || ''[[Despicable Me (franchise)#Panic in the Mailroom (2013)|Panic in the Mailroom]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 11 || ''[[Despicable Me (franchise)#Training Wheels (2013)|Training Wheels]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 12 || ''[[Despicable Me (franchise)#Cro Minion (2015)|Cro Minion]]'' || align=\"right\" rowspan=\"3\" | {{dts|2015|12|8}} || rowspan=\"3\" | ''[[Minions (film)|Minions]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 13 || ''[[Despicable Me (franchise)#Competition (2015)|Competition]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 14 || ''[[Despicable Me (franchise)#Binky Nelson Unpacified (2015)|Binky Nelson Unpacified]]''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | 15 || ''[[Despicable Me (franchise)#Mower Minions (2016)|Mower Min